	$LF
	"(pricewise and 
	[a class=extlink href=http://www.fsf.org/philosophy/free-sw.html rel=nofollow 
		"rightswise
	]a
	").
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"Just remember that if you decide to use a CVS version,
	$LF
	"you need to add libavcodec manually before compiling.
	$LF
]p
[p 
